title: Red-Hot Startup Market Starts to Chill as Investors Turn on Tech Stocks - The Wall Street Journal
content: Red-Hot Startup Market Starts to Chill as Investors Turn on Tech Stocks  The Wall Street Journal
description: Venture capitalists say a reset in investment behavior is starting to take hold, a change that they say is poised to reduce initial public offerings, leave some companies short of funding and crimp valuations.
